*Roditelja* su odgovorni za vaspitanje dece. (Parents are responsible for raising children.)

Dečji svet je najlepši očima *roditelja*. (The children's world is the most beautiful through the eyes of parents.)

*Roditelji* često odlažu svoje želje kako bi ispunili želje dece. (Parents often put aside their wishes in order to fulfill the wishes of their children.)

Mnogi *roditelji* nastoje da svojoj deci pruže najbolje. (Many parents strive to give their children the best.)

*Roditeljstvo* zahteva puno truda i strpljenja. (Parenting requires a lot of effort and patience.)